  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Limestone</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Limestone</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Refine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Refine\">Refined</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> exclusive to the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC and crafted with 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Coral\" title=\"Coral\">Corals</a>. A <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\">Science Machine</a> is required to unlock the recipe. Limestone can be used to craft a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chiminea\" title=\"Chiminea\">Chiminea</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Buoyant_Chiminea\" title=\"Buoyant Chiminea\">Buoyant Chiminea</a>, an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Encrusted_Boat\" title=\"Encrusted Boat\">Encrusted Boat</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tar_Extractor\" title=\"Tar Extractor\">Tar Extractor</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Yard\" title=\"Sea Yard\">Sea Yard</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Lab\" title=\"Sea Lab\">Sea Lab</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone_Suit\" title=\"Limestone Suit\">Limestone Suit</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Coral_Nubbin\" title=\"Coral Nubbin\">Coral Nubbins</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Limestone Walls</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Sea Walls</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ballphin_Palace\" title=\"Ballphin Palace\">Ballphin Palaces</a>. It can however not be used to repair Limestone Walls, as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rocks\" title=\"Rocks\">Rocks</a> can be used to repair <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Stone Walls</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone\" title=\"Limestone\"><img alt=\"Limestone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limestone.png?3c1c7c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sand\" title=\"Sand\"><img alt=\"Sand.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sand.png?43567b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Log\" title=\"Log\"><img alt=\"Log.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Log.png?ddd681\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chiminea\" title=\"Chiminea\"><img alt=\"Chiminea.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Chiminea.png?e3157e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone\" title=\"Limestone\"><img alt=\"