title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Wall\" title=\"Sea Wall\"><img alt=\"Sea Wall.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sea_Wall.png?97ce46\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>6</b></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone\" title=\"Limestone\"><img alt=\"Limestone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limestone.png?3c1c7c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dorsal_Fin\" title=\"Dorsal Fin\"><img alt=\"Dorsal Fin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dorsal_Fin.png?a8602e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ballphin_Palace\" title=\"Ballphin Palace\"><img alt=\"Ballphin Palace.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ballphin_Palace.png?a8ff0b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Limestone is a type of sedimentary rock made of dead shells or coral and other sediments compacted together by heat and pressure over time to make solid rock.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:LimestoneScreenshot.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Limestone on the ground.\"><img alt=\"Limestone on the ground.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/LimestoneScreenshot.png/120px-LimestoneScreenshot.png?6038a9\" width=\"120\" height=\"67\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Limestone on the ground.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DST-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone#DST-0\">DST</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DS-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone#DS-0\">DS</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"RoG-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone#RoG-0\">RoG</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"SW-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone#SW-0\">SW</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Ham-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limestone#Ham-0\">Ham</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"m